CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 18 reads: "5. Miss Willa Rodgers, hostess for the Oswald and Hess Company, served O. and H. samples to delighted homemakers from their booth."
